---
---

<section id="servicios" class="section services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Nuestros Servicios</h2>
      <p>Atención médica integral adaptada a tus necesidades</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="services-grid">
      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="#f5f5f5"/>
            <path d="M24 12v24M12 24h24" stroke="#2c3e50" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Consulta General</h3>
        <p>Atención médica general para diagnóstico y tratamiento de enfermedades comunes. Obtén respuestas rápidas a tus dudas de salud.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="#f5f5f5"/>
            <rect x="16" y="12" width="16" height="24" rx="1" stroke="#2c3e50" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="18" x2="28" y2="18" stroke="#2c3e50" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="23" x2="28" y2="23" stroke="#2c3e50" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Especialidades</h3>
        <p>Acceso a especialistas en cardiología, dermatología, pediatría, psicología y más. Atención especializada cuando la necesitas.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="#f5f5f5"/>
            <rect x="14" y="14" width="20" height="20" rx="2" stroke="#16a085" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="18" y1="22" x2="22" y2="26" stroke="#16a085" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <line x1="22" y1="26" x2="30" y2="18" stroke="#16a085" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Recetas Médicas</h3>
        <p>Recibe recetas médicas digitales válidas directamente en tu correo. Renueva tus medicamentos sin salir de casa.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="#f5f5f5"/>
            <circle cx="24" cy="20" r="6" stroke="#2c3e50" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M14 34c0-5.523 4.477-10 10-10s10 4.477 10 10" stroke="#2c3e50" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Seguimiento Continuo</h3>
        <p>Mantén un historial médico digital y seguimiento de tus tratamientos. Tu médico siempre al tanto de tu evolución.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="#f5f5f5"/>
            <path d="M24 16v16M16 24h16" stroke="#16a085" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="10" stroke="#16a085" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Urgencias</h3>
        <p>Atención prioritaria para casos urgentes. Respuesta inmediata cuando cada minuto cuenta.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="#f5f5f5"/>
            <rect x="16" y="16" width="16" height="16" rx="2" stroke="#2c3e50" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M20 24l2.5 2.5 5.5-5.5" stroke="#2c3e50" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Planes de Bienestar</h3>
        <p>Programas personalizados de prevención y bienestar. Cuida tu salud antes de que surjan problemas.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    background-color: var(--color-background-alt);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--gap-md);
  }

  .service-card {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    border: var(--border-width-thin) solid var(--border-color-light);
    transition: var(--transition-border);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .service-icon {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }
  }
</style>
